OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAG Perarivalan: India top  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcourt frees killer of ex-PM
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FRajiv Gandhi               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, India's Supreme Court has ordered the  
OL,6, release of one of the men convicted of 
OL,7, involvement in the 1991 murder of      
OL,8, former prime minister Rajiv Gandhi.    
OL,10,FAG Perarivalan had spent over 30 years 
OL,11,Fin jail. In 1998, he was given a death 
OL,12,Fsentence, but it was later commuted.   
OL,14,FArrested aged 19, Perarivalan was      
OL,15,Fconvicted of procuring batteries that  
OL,16,Fwere used in the bomb to kill Gandhi.  
OL,18,FThe ex-PM was assassinated by a female 
OL,19,Fsuicide bomber as he addressed an      
OL,20,Felection rally in Tamil Nadu state.    
